name: Kla Henwitch
description:
Kla Henwitch is a friendly demon of the violet order that protects against the woes of general badness, abuse and cheating.

A blue fire breather with the power and energy to destroy your inner demons.

Each guardian demons generated by combining hundreds of unique elements, colors, patterns and randomly generated designs created by the artist. The portraits do not represent evil, but rather are intended to ward off evil like gargoyles on a cathedral.

Collect a demon to protect you against evils and to remind you that you can overcome your personal demons no matter how many or how frightening they might be.
